=\", \"state\" -> \"Boxes\"|>,\"TeXAssistantTemplate\"]\) ", 
   ArcCos[(-$CellContext`k + $CellContext`q 
      Cos[$CellContext`\[Theta]]) ($CellContext`k^2 + $CellContext`q^2 - 
      2 $CellContext`k $CellContext`q Cos[$CellContext`\[Theta]])^
     Rational[-1, 2]]],
  Editable->False]], "Print",
